thread.title: Several killed after a van hits crowd in Germany

title: Several killed after a van hits crowd in Germany
text:
Several killed after a van hits crowd in Germany   00:37 
A man drove a van into a group of people sitting outside a popular restaurant in the old city centre of Muenster in western Germany on Saturday, killing several of them before taking his own life, police said. Lucy Fielder reports
